eya_def_tools.data_models.result.Result
Collection of results a quantity along specific dimensions.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the result. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the result. Default is None. assessment_period (Optional[AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)]): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is None. dimensions (Optional[list[ResultsDimension(StrEnum)]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the result statistic. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the result statistic. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[list[UnionType[float, int, str]], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id (str): Unique ID of the wind resource assessment within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind resource assessment. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind resource assessment. Default is None. results (WindResourceResults): Results of the wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceResults
Wind resource assessment results at measurement locations.
Attributes: wind_speed (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates at the measurement location(s)in metre per second. probability (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term probability distribution estimates at the measurement location(s), such as wind speed probability distributions or joint wind speed and direction frequency distributions, as dimensionless values. Default is None. turbulence_intensity (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term turbulence intensity estimates at the measurement location(s) as dimensionless values. Default is None. wind_shear_exponent (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term power law wind shear exponent estimates at the measurement location(s). Default is None. temperature (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term temperature estimates at the measurement location(s) in degree C. Default is None. air_density (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term air density estimates at the measurement location(s) in kilogram per cubic metre. Default is None.
